{"tid":1388362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"都話左一早要咁打","createTime":"2019-07-30T16:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:03:20.000Z","uid":249376,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b762485f68269cd55965764f1ea9090b12fceb45","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"之前衝突結束檢討果陣已經講左好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好次次都鬥集結人多先黎打 睇落去氣勢係好勁但打果陣真係另一回事<br />\n今晚完全可以印證到<br />\n300vs10 效果係&gt;&gt;&gt; 3000vs100<br />\n對面陣容戰術咁有系統遠攻又易發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要贏就梗係要用少數圍毆<br />\n要係佢地人數集結到可以排成一個陣之前就追撚鳩住佢地黎打<br />\n今日係差在無人撲低佢地其中一個<br />\n如果有 打撚死佢地都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8726de2077bc592bd51aa39f3358917eb207cbe","tid":1388362,"uid":108337,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"襲警打人坐2年咋<br />\n暴動比人打到仆街要坐10年阿<br />\n<br />\n暴動仲要係對面冇損失, 自方全滅"},{"pid":"81304756a1675efec9feb0ca04c768e487be4be8","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:37:29.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"0d0c9c7c3743e4ca14dee0115063f483df8cbf29","tid":1388362,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:38:01.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},{"pid":"8be9928ad4af26eb28722cc2d2bbae12f181acca","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"358508d4c478dc70c85028eb174e5f3c9e954e6d","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"07dd9682fbd8a681f676f0a27148c9ead9a6f389","tid":1388362,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8726de2077bc592bd51aa39f3358917eb207cbe","tid":1388362,"uid":108337,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"襲警打人坐2年咋<br />\n暴動比人打到仆街要坐10年阿<br />\n<br />\n暴動仲要係對面冇損失, 自方全滅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4f8fc3982dac86d96ece7efc32a3b97c710e2a","tid":1388362,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8726de2077bc592bd51aa39f3358917eb207cbe","tid":1388362,"uid":108337,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"襲警打人坐2年咋<br />\n暴動比人打到仆街要坐10年阿<br />\n<br />\n暴動仲要係對面冇損失, 自方全滅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892560d4cf01b85876b3d781d8cc5d2e147994f3","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"11570f87e3f588c210c96a903c3419929e3da661","tid":1388362,"uid":101392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"遍地開花玩游擊hit and run<br />\n尤其港島<br />\n好多目標佢哋要守，警力會分散晒<br />\n<br />\n譬如前一日放風去以下地點：<br />\n警總、中聯辦、政府總部<br />\n佢地已經要分兵駐守三個地方<br />\n<br />\n當日金鐘站集合 到時前線先再決定去邊度<br />\n<br />\n可以突襲去D唔喺個list度嘅地方：<br />\n譬如：外交部特派專員公署、金紫荊、律政中心、中區警署、西區警署、禮賓府、前行政長官辦公室、律政司司長官邸<br />\n<br />\n夠人甚至可以分途出擊<br />\n佢哋唔知守邊 度度都唔夠兵力<br />\n突襲完成即走去下個check point<br />\n唔好留低俾人拉"},{"pid":"47df06a1d268e461fb64bca8907b3a16ed1f5147","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"04909116c1b94e3c5476efa89798c0c87a2d19f3","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:52:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"2b9434e0408ae8d426b1c3bce7bd4ab4da83d65d","tid":1388362,"uid":249376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n戰術要升級"},{"pid":"f1d395bafbf1887c656876fb15d3e1d390e65814